roue tourne\' and \'Je te promets\'. This album earned her various prizes, awards and nominations, including \'Best French-speaking Artist\' at the MTV Europe Music Awards, \'French Revelation of the Year\' and \'Best Duo\' at the NRJ Music Awards. to its place after the tournament.<br \\/> He approaches the rock and\\u2026 succeeds in pulling Excalibur out without the slightest effort. The rumblings of the crowd rise, and the gathering approaches the boy who is going to be designated the new king of Britain.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"1\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"1\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
